item.title: SoftLayer_Container_Product_Order_Attribute_Organization
item.description: SoftLayer_Container_Product_Order_Attribute_Organization Datatype Description This is the datatype that needs to be populated and sent to SoftLayer_Product_Order::placeOrder. The SoftLayer_Container_Product_Order_Attribute_Organization datatype contains the organization information. Local address The address information of the contact. Type: SoftLayer_Container_Product_Order_Attribute_Address faxNumber The fax number associated with an organization. This is an optional value. Type: string organizationName The name of an organization. Type: string
